# Shell scripts MUST stay LF - a CRLF entrypoint.sh makes the Linux container
# try to exec "/bin/sh\r" and fail to start ("Application exec likely failed",
# no Python output). core.autocrlf=true on Windows checkouts reintroduces CRLF
# without this. Pin all shell scripts (and the entrypoint specifically) to LF.
*.sh text eol=lf
entrypoint.sh text eol=lf
